<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8426195>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Morphological details of some Cryptotropidae. A, stylet protruding from the genital atrium of Renschetrema sp. B, C, eggs released from the uterus of Pseudocryptotropa surniculi." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8426195/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8426201>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Position of copulatory pouch in the four new species described in this study. A, Cryptotropa acanthosauri. B, Pseudocryptotropa surniculi. C, Pseudocryptotropa testilobata. D, Paracryptotropa peruviana." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8426201/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8426203>
    dc:description "Figure 6. New species of Pseudocryptotropa. A, Pseudocryptotropa surniculi, ventral view of the holotype. B, P. surniculi, testes of a paratype. C, Pseudocryptotropa testilobata, ventral view of the holotype. D, P. testilobata, testes of a paratype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8426203/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8426205>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Scanning electron micrographs of Pseudocryptotropa surniculi. A, total view, ventral. B, total view, dorsal. C, oral sucker. D, genital atrium on dorsal side of the body.E, excretory pore. F, tegumental spines on dorsal side of the anterior part of the body. G, tegumental spines on ventral side of the anterior part of the body." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8426205/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

